note: 60 spins around the Sun have shown me that I know less than I thought I did when I was younger. Left of center by a little but want to understand all points of view. Husband to amazing wife, father to two dogs and a cat. Sometime Medium writer and former podcaster.  News and politics junkie who wants to go into a program to rid myself of that harmful addiction. Music, books, old TV shows and movies that drive my younger wife mad.

name: Being a decent human is free.
